ZH: 今天是星期日。
EN: Today is Sunday.

ZH: 明日天气会很好。
EN: The weather will be nice tomorrow.

ZH: 这个新闻发生在昨日。
EN: This news occurred yesterday.

ZH: 日出时，景色很美。
EN: The view is beautiful at sunrise.

ZH: 请问今日还有什么活动吗？
EN: Do you have any plans for today?

ZH: 昨日我们去爬山了。
EN: We went hiking yesterday.

ZH: 请记得今日下午与我联系。
EN: Remember to contact me this afternoon.

ZH: 我日常做饭。
EN: I cook daily.

ZH: 他每日锻炼。
EN: He exercises daily.

ZH: 今日的课程很有意思。
EN: Today's class is very interesting.

ZH: 请查看明日的议程。
EN: Please check tomorrow's schedule.

ZH: 日落时，天空变得很美丽。
EN: The sky becomes beautiful at sunset.

ZH: 每日喝水是很重要的。
EN: Drinking water daily is important.

ZH: 我明日要面试。
EN: I have an interview tomorrow.

ZH: 警察在昨日抓了小偷。
EN: The police arrested the thief yesterday.

ZH: 日晒雨淋，他都来上班。
EN: Rain or shine, he comes to work.

ZH: 今日我们要去看电影。
EN: We are going to watch a movie today.

ZH: 每逢星期日，我们都会去教堂。
EN: Every Sunday, we go to church.

ZH: 明日早饭我来做。
EN: I will cook breakfast tomorrow.

ZH: 前日她买了新衣服。
EN: She bought new clothes the day before yesterday.
